Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.19,Default,Account,0,0,0,,Three-point increase!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:03.70,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Buy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:04.44,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,everything you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:06.65,Default,Account,0,0,0,,We've found a ship carrying copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.03,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Acquire it. Pay double if you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:10.65,Default,SA,0,0,0,,Emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:15.57,Default,SA,0,0,0,,The church is backing the Holy Capital's effort to issue new currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.15,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,The exchange rate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:21.08,Default,SA,0,0,0,,Twenty-eight old-currency gold will get ten of the new.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.96,Default,SA,0,0,0,,The possession or use of old currency will be forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.93,Default,SA,0,0,0,,I've also heard that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:29.17,Default,SA,0,0,0,,they plan to issue more of the new currency than required by the exchange rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.99,Default,Duchess,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:32.15,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.59,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,they're replacing 10,000 in old currency with 5,000 of the new,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:41.04,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,and then claiming the new amount is worth 14,000 in old currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:42.94,Default,Duchess,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that mean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:47.33,Default,Duchess,0,0,0,,the government makes a 4,000-gold profit, as measured by the old standard?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.44,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,It does indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.79,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,It's quite clever, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.03,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll be able to maintain the new currency's value at 2.8?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:02.97,Default,Royal Guard,0,0,0,,All the soldiers and knights in our territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:05.25,Default,Royal Guard,0,0,0,,654 in total, have gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.71,Default,Royal Guard,0,0,0,,The Ashen King brings his royal knights and axe brigades.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:12.36,Default,Royal Guard,0,0,0,,The Mountain Country's heavy cavalry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Treetop Country's archers will also arrive soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:17.43,Default,General,0,0,0,,What of enemy movement?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:19.94,Default,RG,0,0,0,,Holding position in the forest, at only several hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:22.14,Default,RG,0,0,0,,It appears that they're slow to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.10,Default,Mercenary Captain,0,0,0,,Maybe they're afraid of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:27.78,Default,General,0,0,0,,How many have you brought?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.86,Default,Mercenary Captain,0,0,0,,Four hundred veterans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.61,Default,Mercenary Captain,0,0,0,,You'll be paying us well for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:36.36,Default,Retainer,0,0,0,,My lord, dinner is prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:40.49,Default,Retainer,0,0,0,,The local landowners have donated barrels of strong drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.79,Default,Retainer,0,0,0,,Twenty barrels of high-quality iced wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:49.34,Default,General,0,0,0,,So that is how they hope to keep us from trampling their fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.71,Default,General,0,0,0,,I'll give some to the mercenaries as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.84,Default,Ms,0,0,0,,It's one of the lady's students!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:57.85,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:59.30,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:03.72,Default,MS,0,0,0,,What I learned from our teacher's lessons has kept me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.06,Default,MS,0,0,0,,But why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.48,Default,Mb,0,0,0,,We're compiling a book of new teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.98,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,The Crimson Scholar's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.68,Default,WNK,0,0,0,,Our spies report that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:19.45,Default,WNK,0,0,0,,she's making many blasphemous books in the Iron Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.12,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:26.29,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,The Inquisition has judged her to be a demon! A blasphemer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:31.29,Default,WNK,0,0,0,,The serfs have been crossing the border into the Iron Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.72,Default,WNK,0,0,0,,At this rate, my country...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Night Country will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:37.97,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Then steal them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:39.97,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,A surprise attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.23,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,They'll be focused on the punitive force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:48.39,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,In the meantime, we'll ambush the Iron Country and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:53.86,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,I'll share the darkness in my right eye with the entire country!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:53.86,OP,,0,0,0,,{OP}{First white frame}
