Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.79,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to be annoying for you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.79,0:03:11.75,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I don't mind being conceited
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.80,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hide a tree in a forest, they say
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.30,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}It started with a little mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.30,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's redo our meeting from there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.77,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's oppose the strand of time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.52,0:03:33.73,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Strength alone is no weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.81,0:03:41.90,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}You taught me that just now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.90,0:03:47.41,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to show you what lies
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.41,0:03:53.62,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}beyond these days
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.17,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}The wind is strong
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.26,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I'm sure you know that too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.26,0:04:04.09,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I can't fly
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.09,0:04:10.89,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Sharing makes you dependant
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.89,0:04:14.06,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now, take my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.61,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hold it tight
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.61,0:04:20.90,OP,bord,0,0,0,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now...
