Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:32.58,Default,WK,0,0,0,,Then we'll maintain a strong defensive formation and wait for snow to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.88,Default,General,0,0,0,,I'll have the winter gear handed out at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.92,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Could I ask you to minimize the casualties?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,The army of the Central Nations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,will be at least 20,000 strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.05,Default,WK,0,0,0,,We'll be fortunate to field even 4,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:51.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,It'll depend on their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'll ensure as few casualties as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.98,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Message from the southern ice seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.57,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.36,Default,WK,0,0,0,,Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.84,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,We're not sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but based on what we can see, at least 1,500!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.87,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,Has something happened to the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:15.28,Default,Y,0,0,0,,No, not to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.08,Default,WK,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.97,Default,WK,0,0,0,,We have no troops to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.17,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.84,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I'll take care of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:27.64,Default,Y,0,0,0,,But would you be upset if I said I don't want to fight the demons either?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.14,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:38.44,Default,WK,0,0,0,,We must avoid a fight on two fronts at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.23,Default,B,0,0,0,,My king...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.98,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Thank you, Winter King.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.03,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Are you the Financial Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.66,Default,FM,0,0,0,,Yes, though only just appointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.79,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to visit so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.88,Default,FM,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.12,Default,FM,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.48,Default,FM,0,0,0,,You're the one who's been playing a game across the whole continent,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.96,Default,FM,0,0,0,, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.34,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.30,Default,FM,0,0,0,,If I were the one playing, I'd visit in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.93,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,You were the one who established that tariff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.06,Default,FM,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.48,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.69,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Well, let's negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.40,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,I have four things to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.32,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,I'll summarize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:28.70,Default,First,0,0,0,,First, I'd like you to give the Alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:32.12,Default,First,0,0,0,,an exclusive exemption from the tariff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.18,Default,FM,0,0,0,,An exemption?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.92,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,The exemption would only apply to goods passing through your realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,not to any that are purchased within.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:42.29,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,That would prevent the exemption from affecting your economy, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.79,Default,FM,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.26,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Second, lease rights for Bright Light Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:52.98,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,I'd like to lease part of the island in the same way a lord is granted a manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.22,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,In this matter, I represent another party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.84,Default,FM,0,0,0,,Who would want that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.66,Default,FM,0,0,0,,The only thing there is salt—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.69,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Third,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:04.90,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,are you familiar with the banking organizations within the Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:08.57,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,I'd like permission to establish banks and other Alliance facilities
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,within your three nations' capitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.16,Default,FM,0,0,0,,That would be wonderful, but well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:18.38,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Fourth, we're prepared to purchase
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.54,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,your entire potato stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.75,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:28.05,Default,FM,0,0,0,,Um, the Inquisition has banned potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:36.80,Default,FM,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Central Nations have reissued the currency to try to raise its value.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.88,Default,FM,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's not going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:43.31,Default,FM,0,0,0,,{\i1}The value of food products, such as wheat, is far more stable...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:49.40,Default,FM,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the Alliance is the group with the most wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:58.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's the army's job to end a war,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's the king's job to find a place for it to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:06.44,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm a Hero, not a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.67,Default,Y,0,0,0,,So I couldn't find the place for it to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:13.68,Default,M,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you'll accompany me to the other side of the hill, that's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.43,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I definitely want to see it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:21.93,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You and me, the Knight and the Old Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.62,Default,Y,0,0,0,,the King, the Maid Sisters, and the Head Maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:28.20,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Mage, Gate City, the Southern Nations,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.19,Default,Y,0,0,0,,and everyone in Winter's Pass Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:36.24,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I want the Central Nations and the demons to see it as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.98,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just destroy and kill, without creating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.42,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Azure Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:54.05,Default,Y,0,0,0,,They're equipped for long-distance travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.52,Default,Y,0,0,0,,And they have provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.60,Default,Y,0,0,0,,If I'm going to make them withdraw, that's where I should aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.02,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.44,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,You included me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'm finally out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.54,Default,M,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:32.74,Default,M,0,0,0,,and tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:35.13,Default,M,0,0,0,,That was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.22,Default,M,0,0,0,,What's wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.58,Default,M,0,0,0,,Head Maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.20,Default,M,0,0,0,,Let's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.48,Default,HM,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,The battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.80,Default,M,0,0,0,,What are you doing, insect?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.66,Default,HM,0,0,0,,I'm no insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:06.16,Default,M,0,0,0,,Oh, but you {\i1}are{\i0} an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,You'll see when you're flat on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:13.55,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Her Majesty would never have such a crude laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:16.13,Default,M,0,0,0,,This is how I'll be from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.59,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Her Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is brilliant, an intellectual,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,logical, calm, cynical,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:28.44,Default,HM,0,0,0,,pragmatic, but still has a cute smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.23,Default,HM,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}my{\i0} master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.96,Default,HM,0,0,0,,She's lazy, and she hates to change or wash her clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.28,Default,HM,0,0,0,,She can't clean or cook, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:38.78,Default,HM,0,0,0,,But she is the one I chose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:47.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,My strength is far greater than the Fanged Beasts, yet you match me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.18,Default,M,0,0,0,,But you are still a mere demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.34,Default,M,0,0,0,,I went easy on you in hopes that you might serve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.30,Default,HM,0,0,0,,I am a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.18,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.28,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,{\an8}Communication channel established.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.89,Default,Y,0,0,0,,{\an8}I never get used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.24,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.34,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,The Demon King is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.00,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.00,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,I'll act in your stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.08,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Once I've dealt with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you must destroy the gate with the strongest spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.18,Default,Y,0,0,0,,If I do that, no one will be able to go to the Demon Realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.51,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.30,Default,Y,0,0,0,,It's all right to destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:48.82,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,...needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:54.18,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,She needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:00.19,Default,FM,0,0,0,,You aren't interested in the wheat as a trade good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.08,Default,FM,0,0,0,,But as a pseudo-currency!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:03.98,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:08.46,Default,FM,0,0,0,,And you plan to invest that wheat in the Southern Triads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.87,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Indeed, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.71,Default,FM,0,0,0,,A-And you're after...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.67,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{\i1}The continent functions as one international market due to its unified currency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,{\i1}So when inflation begins,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}throwing around additional coinage in one nation accomplishes nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.74,Default,M,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also, if you want increased competitiveness with the surrounding regions,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's best to have more than one currency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.77,Default,FM,0,0,0,,A dual-currency system...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.38,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:41.66,Default,FM,0,0,0,,True, with the Central Nations' economy weakened, now is the perfect time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.50,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Which naturally means our next step
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,will be to invest in an emerging market with growth potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:49.83,Default,FM,0,0,0,,Are you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,intending to go beyond our territorial waters and open trade relations with demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:56.08,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.75,Default,FM,0,0,0,,Why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.26,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Because I'm a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:04.59,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,Everyone has an opinion as to what's right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.14,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,We will never see eye-to-eye on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone wants to be a little happier than they currently are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:15.68,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,So isn't our job to compromise on that one point,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.02,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,and then to trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.94,Default,FM,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:23.94,Default,DP,0,0,0,,I ask that you consider this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.76,Default,FM,0,0,0,,H-Horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.62,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,She's the Dragon Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:38.58,Default,Ym,0,0,0,,A representative of Gate City, the one place in the Demon Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,where humans and demons coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Total number of demons: 2,670.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiating range-finding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Locking on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Spell-decompression algorithm in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,15% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,37%.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,59%.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,81%.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Designate current area as target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Removing conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To save the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had to use Time Stretch and multiple compressions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to save up all these spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what that took? How many years?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.78,Default,Y,0,0,0,,She's losing her cool again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:25.78,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,{\an8}When something happens to the Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}my job is to go him and grant his wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:30.38,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Is she seriously teleporting each of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:32.68,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you understand what it did to my pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}that twilight day when I could do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.52,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Can you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:48.61,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:49.94,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:51.50,Default,Y,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.58,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Maziodyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.58,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Mass destruction confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:40.58,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Maybe I overdid it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.50,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Use your magic to fly into the pillar of smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:51.94,Default,Major,0,0,0,,Damn White Night! Only barbarians would consider a surprise attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.84,Default,Major,0,0,0,,Even if they outnumber us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.58,Default,Major,0,0,0,,we must destroy them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.81,Default,MS,0,0,0,,You mustn't be impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.73,Default,MS,0,0,0,,We're facing their cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:05.38,Default,MS,0,0,0,,The only countermeasure for their mobility
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is to isolate them and work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.12,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Enemy approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:16.38,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,They'll arrive in a minute or so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.74,Default,MS,0,0,0,,All forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.29,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Ready crossbows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:26.50,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Primary targets are stationary or any dismounted soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.17,Default,MS,0,0,0,,The enemy is comprised of light cavalry, which emphasizes speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:32.47,Default,MS,0,0,0,,They lack the plate mail to stop our crossbows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.47,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Don't force any risky shots! Aim for the center of the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.56,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.31,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.11,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Why are you stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.86,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Enemy trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.71,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Use your speed to push through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.54,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,All troops, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.21,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The enemy numbers few!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.46,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.92,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.97,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Use your mobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:18.68,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Push forward and spread the rear lines to the left and right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.10,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Keep firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:25.14,Default,MS,0,0,0,,New conscripts are to divide themselves between weapon loading and defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.34,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Defense squads are to eliminate any troops
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that make it into our trenches, move any horses, and keep them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.45,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Archers and loaders, concentrate all fire on the right flank!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.90,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Our side attack is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.58,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The right flank is weakening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.66,Default,OEG,0,0,0,,Good! Send all our forces in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.41,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.04,Default,Major,0,0,0,,The enemy is heading for the left flank!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.00,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Then the right flank drove them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.38,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Our defenses are on a sloping hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.90,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Any cavalry that makes it past the front lines won't break through,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:18:02.39,Default,MS,0,0,0,,but they'll be drawn into a small, cramped area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:07.00,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Now it's time for us to do our jobs, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.23,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.02,Default,MS,0,0,0,,check your bows once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.53,Default,MS,0,0,0,,It's time for our assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.54,Default,Y,0,0,0,,It's getting brighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.10,Default,Y,0,0,0,,What's this wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.23,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.60,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The Demon Realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.72,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:44.18,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The Demon Realm is {\i1}underground?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:47.00,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Yes, it's not a separate world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.61,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,It's connected to the Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:52.61,Default,Y,0,0,0,,What's happening with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.48,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,She's nearly become the King of Evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:56.92,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The King of Evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.49,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,But the Demon King is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.40,Default,Y,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.12,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,She's waiting for you, you damn virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.16,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,Move your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:09.84,Default,Ma,0,0,0,,She's at the center of the Demon King's castle, at the lowest level...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:14.54,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Your Majesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:17.40,Default,HM,0,0,0,,just try once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.38,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Remember how black,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.55,Default,HM,0,0,0,,fluffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and warm it looked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.36,Default,M,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.80,Default,M,0,0,0,,{\an8}Trying to buy time is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:46.83,Default,HM,0,0,0,,If she comes out again, I'm going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This body is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.83,Default,M,0,0,0,,{\an8}I am the Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.50,Default,HM,0,0,0,,But even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.00,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I'll go straight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.28,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Accelerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.80,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I've never seen magic particles like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:13.54,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Is the Demon King really this strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:18.48,Default,General,0,0,0,,The Central Nations' army has begun a full conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.36,Default,General,0,0,0,,They have 40,000 all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:22.76,Default,General,0,0,0,,Of those, 28,000 are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.62,Default,General,0,0,0,,9,000 are cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,So what did we send them today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:31.62,Default,General,0,0,0,,Thirty barrels of iced wine, three boars, six pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:32.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:35.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,They'll hold another banquet tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,Next we'll need horse fodder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.46,Default,General,0,0,0,,Fodder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:45.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,With that many horses, they'll require a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:48.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,This time, inform more farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:50.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,The army's here, and if you have no fodder for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,they could hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,And sell them the dried grass and oats we prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Giving it to them is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.65,Default,General,0,0,0,,What's the point of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,The grass and oats
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,have been soaked with filthy water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,Just enough to gradually sicken the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:09.32,Default,General,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.90,Default,General,0,0,0,,{\pos(722.667,695.333)}That'll make it harder to start a conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.83,Default,K,0,0,0,,I feel bad for the horses,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,but I'm sure they'd prefer that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,to death on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.70,Default,MS,0,0,0,,The Iron-Arm King has
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.09,Default,MS,0,0,0,,instructed us to treat the wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.09,Default,MS,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,719.333)}Don't help our side alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638.667,720.667)}Start with the worst off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and use a handkerchief, so the doctors know the priorities!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,712.667)}Move any lightly wounded to the outside tents!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the citizens help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,716.667)}Move the moderately wounded within the Convent,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(902.667,703.333)}treat their wounds, and use distilled alcohol for disinfection!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:43.57,Default,Major,0,0,0,,You're a general now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.30,Default,MS,0,0,0,,A g-general?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.20,Default,Major,0,0,0,,In this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.42,Default,Major,0,0,0,,that's the term for soldiers who perform above the call of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:52.30,Default,MS,0,0,0,,I wasn't even thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:57.36,Default,MS,0,0,0,,I was only doing as I was taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.79,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.28,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Our forces sustained 18 fatalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:03.60,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,and 221 are wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:06.32,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The White Night suffered 304 fatalities
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:08.50,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,with 892 injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:10.26,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,450 prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:11.14,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,In addition,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.96,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,712.667)}several enemy troops escaped into the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.27,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,and we are in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:19.15,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The one-eyed man we believe to be their commander is among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:26.28,Default,MS,0,0,0,,Give anyone who can still move a meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,let them rest, then send them on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:34.02,Default,MS,0,0,0,,I'll keep watch on the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:40.08,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:50.39,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:57.31,Default,M,0,0,0,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.12,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Demon King...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:00.94,Default,HM,0,0,0,,Be careful, Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:02.94,Default,HM,0,0,0,,That isn't really her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:14.78,Default,HM,0,0,0,,The evil spirits of the ancient Demon Kings have corrupted her.
